into my hands[deletion][unclear]xxxx[/unclear][/deletion] fragments of [insertion]two MS one of which had been operated upon by M[superscript]r[/superscript] Hayter & the other by D[superscript]r[/superscript]Sickler &[/insertion] [deletion][unclear]xxxx[/unclear][/deletion] which (the principal
